            "answer_text": "The spine has 3 natural curves. Maintaining these curves keeps the stress to the intervertebral discs to a minimum. Removing these curves will increase the stress to the discs increasing the chances of bulging, herniation or worse. Proper posture will include these three curves. Seek balance. Cheers! ",
